targets.query: SELECT count("state") FROM "autogen"."build" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^pull.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "job_name"
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*4.6.*unit.*/  AND "state_int" = 0 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.6.*unit.*/  AND "state_int" = 1 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.6.*unit*/  AND "state_int" = 2 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.6.*unit.*/  AND "state_int" = 4 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*4.6.*e2e.*/  AND "state_int" = 0 ) AND $timeFilter

SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*unit.*/  AND "state_int" = 4 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~ /.*4.7.*e2e.*/  AND "state_int" = 0 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*e2e.*/  AND "state_int" = 1 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*e2e.*/  AND "state_int" = 2 ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("state") FROM "build"  WHERE ("job_name" =~  /.*4.7.*e2e.*/  AND "state_int" = 4 ) AND $timeFilter
select count("state_int") as "passed"  FROM "build" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^pull.*.e2e.*/ and "state_int" = 0 ) GROUP BY pull_request
select count("state_int") as "failed"  FROM "build" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^pull.*.e2e.*/ and "state_int" = 2) GROUP BY pull_request
select count("state_int") as "aborted"  FROM "build" WHERE ("job_name" =~ /^pull.*.e2e.*/ and "state_int" = 3) GROUP BY pull_request
